# OmniRoam 仓库忽略规则：通用构建产物 + Catkin / PlatformIO 生成目录。
# ROS 路径说明见 scripts/setup_ros1.bash 顶部注释。
#
# Prerequisites
*.d

# Object files
*.o
*.ko
*.obj
*.elf

# Linker output
*.ilk
*.map
*.exp

# Precompiled Headers
*.gch
*.pch

# Libraries
*.lib
*.a
*.la
*.lo

# Shared objects (inc. Windows DLLs)
*.dll
*.so
*.so.*
*.dylib

# Executables
*.exe
*.out
*.app
*.i*86
*.x86_64
*.hex

# Debug files
*.dSYM/
*.su
*.idb
*.pdb

# Kernel Module Compile Results
*.mod*
*.cmd
.tmp_versions/
modules.order
Module.symvers
Mkfile.old
dkms.conf

# debug information files
*.dwo

# ROS 1 Catkin (build artifacts; keep catkin_ws/src/)
catkin_ws/build/
catkin_ws/devel/
catkin_ws/install/
catkin_ws/logs/
software/ros/catkin_ws/build/
software/ros/catkin_ws/devel/
software/ros/catkin_ws/install/
software/ros/catkin_ws/logs/

# PlatformIO（simplerobotic/ 内另有 .gitignore）
simplerobotic/.pio/

# OmniRoam 根目录 start/restart 脚本写入的 PID 与日志
.omniroam/

# HostPC local runtime settings and compiled C backend
software/backend/hostpc-c
software/backend/hostpc-users.cauth
software/backend/hostpc-settings.json

# HostPC root runtime settings
hostpc-users.cauth
hostpc-settings.json
# macOS metadata
.DS_Store
._*
__MACOSX/

# HostPC Go API build output
software/backend-go/hostpc-api
# Runtime logs written at repository root
yolo_obstacle_detector.log
yolo_obstacle_detector.pid

# HostPC sensitive runtime files
hostpc-auth-secret
hostpc-users.db
backend/hostpc-auth-secret
backend/hostpc-users.db
backend/hostpc-users.sqlite

# Frontend dependencies
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/.vite/
frontend/.vue-global-types/

# C control core build output
backend/amseokbot-control-core
backend/hostpc-c

# Local AI assistant skills
SKILL.md
skill.md
**/SKILL.md
**/skill.md

# Runtime secrets and local databases
*secret*
*.db
*.sqlite
.env

# Local IDE cache
.vs/
**/.vs/
